data.title: 1925 Brabant Dr, Plano, TX 75025
data.meta_description: 1925 Brabant Dr, Plano, TX 75025 is pending. Zillow has 34 photos of this 4 beds, 3 baths, 2,715 Square Feet single family home with a list price of $725,000.
data.text: A SHOW STOPPER completely renovated 2 story house on a corner lot in a great west Plano neighborhood. 2715 Sqf 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 3 living and 2 dining areas. Beautiful 9 foot double doors will lead you into a light and bright open floorplan with vaulted ceiling, windows all around and a grand staircase. Spacious main area, features living room with fireplace, dining room and a family room, great for entertaining. A large kitchen with all new white cabinets, quartz countertops, backsplash, SS appliances, gas cooking, vent hood, walk-in pantry, island and breakfast area overlooking the fenced back yard. Primary bedroom on main floor with ensuite bath offers a stand alone tub, separate shower, dual sinks vanity and walk in closet. Upstairs you will find a game room 3 bedrooms and one full bath. A mud room, utility room, half a bath and rear entry 2 car garage. High end designer finishes , wood floors, lighting, fixtures, pattern carpet and much more. Plano ISD. Parks and shopping.
